&amp;#x200B;

I ended up going out with the girl I met at work not long after, and we're very in love. We have been dating since. I did move very fast after. Sometimes I think about how I ended it with my ex though, and feel bad. I'm sure she has since moved on, as have I. Maybe it's just selfish of me to think about it and maybe I'm bothered with the image of myself being an asshole, rather than the actual thing I did... I'm not very sure. All I know is I feel bad about how I did it, but not sure what else I could have done. Maybe waited a day? Probably. But it's in the past now. 

